it.polito.dp2.RNS

Interface VehicleReader

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IdentifiedEntityReader

    public interface VehicleReader
extends IdentifiedEntityReader
    An interface for reading information about a vehicle in the RNS system. For a vehicle, the unique id inherited from IdentifiedEntityReader is the vehicle plate id, which is a string made only of uppercase alphabetic characters and digits. In addition to the id, a vehicle is also characterized by its type, its entry time, its origin and destination places, its current position (which is a place too), and its state.
